data.description: Nestled in the community of Spring Grove, this home invites you to experience luxury living at its finest. Have you always wanted a kitchen with tons of cabinet space and a large island that is perfect for entertaining?? This home checks all those boxes!! This kitchen will definitely impress anyone who loves to entertain or cook. Downstairs you have a bedroom with full bath perfect for your guests or as an office space.Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms and a large loft perfect for movie night! To add to this amazing neighborhood Spring Grove also has a RV/Boat Storage lot! You really can have it all with this home!!!
